{"tid":1244811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621發夢須知！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T06:50:07.000Z","uid":264114,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22c3af523ba3c805de5dbe4a5959f0427a251a32","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">只係一個今個月發咗幾次夢既人，有啲野想講。<br />\n雨傘果陣只係個讀緊中學既和理非，點解依家會變咗發夢勇武既一份子？因為一百萬人二百萬人政府都唔撚理你囉仆街，其他地方如果有二百萬人遊行個政府收得皮啦，我地呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好問621發夢做咩，依家唔關明日大嶼事，621出黎係因為620 5pm deadline 777都未回應</span></span><br />\n無論發夢做咩都好，要621聚咗人先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">621四大訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撒回，釋放義士，警方濫權，平反暴動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不篤灰，不割蓆，不自己人打自己人<br />\n勇有勇既做，和有和既做，政黨有政黨既做，ok？？</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔知點贏，我淨係知我地一定要贏咋屌。<br />\n大家撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">夢遊要着咩衫</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1.black bloc<br />\n2.長褲，咪比我見到短褲短裙，起碼遮到膝頭，唔想有人因為仆親撞到而傷<br />\n3.可以既手都包埋，落外套/手袖</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">wasabi蛋</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1.泳鏡<br />\n2.唔好帶普通口罩<br />\n3.唔好跑，急步行<br />\n4.閉氣，只要食咗一啖就會開始咳，越咳越食越多，惡性循環<br />\n5.每人至少一支水，飲/沖/倒落wasabi度<br />\n6.注意風向，唔岩就唔好掟，最好淋落去啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔想/唔敢做前線既你地，我地絕對明白，但你地只要願意企前少少，哪怕只係一小步，已經比到前線好大信心。(唔好阻塞逃生路線)</span><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔撚知發夢仲有咩準備，只係好想大家發一場好夢，醒返可以見到好好既香港。只想講句加油。<br />\n<br />\n發過夢既你地請撐住，我都好攰，身心都好攰，但香港人唔會咁易放棄架係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未完成義士遺願，一日都唔可以停止發夢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">夢入面見啦大家</span>"},{"pid":"0fc23acc5644a9053d4d9f8649e7690f4bff34ed","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"(求屌醒)621要做乜？我乜都唔知 點解要出？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99a0c2a1309c6ee617be921c4304526c39367cb1","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkR4Vfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkR4Vfq.png&h=4a3bd3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yovJrm5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyovJrm5.png&h=28b4f498&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxNcjG6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxNcjG6.png&h=a5e24628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"102d8e7ff3c7695c27f416d657285d978c690004","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"939fa213cabeacfb77dbec1a663590bd68b8ef47","tid":1244811,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b6704e70c27c3281f3f3c69ba38dfb22a5038f9","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9d2d0f68b65c12300b04377db893017d40cb8e6","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b831099ee23f6f84bc68ab46f945c6323b936005","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f516315d97748929a714b35e38b44b10244e9a1c","tid":1244811,"uid":264114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"298f47099b1598c5e2f8942588ed6630fb7e43f3","tid":1244811,"uid":193972,"like":0,"disli